<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 wr-brainbreaks content">
                <div class="row"><img style="margin-top: -15px" src="~/Images/brainbreaks/brainBreaks_banner_01.jpg" alt="Skoolbo Brain Brakes" class="im-responsive"></div>
                <div class="space-10"> </div>
                <p>Skoolbo Brain Breaks includes 20 great songs for students to dance along to in class. Teachers simply beam them up on a data projector, interactive whiteboard or a TV. They are a two-minute burst of activity between lessons. Skoolbo Brain Breaks are ideal for ages 5 to 8.</p>
                <div class="row show-destop">
                    <div class="col-md-5 pull-right col-md-offset-right-1">
                        <div class="space-10"></div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="show-video"><img src="~/Images/brainbreaks/VideoBrainBreaks.png" alt="Skoolbo Brain Brakes" class="im-responsive video-brain-breaks"></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 pull-left">
                        <div class="space-10">         </div>
                        <h4 class="margin-top-0"><strong> Key Pedagogies</strong></h4>
                        <ul style="list-style-type: disc">
                            <li>Encourages singing, dancing and drama</li>
                            <li>Develops gross motor skills</li>
                            <li>Promotes vocabulary and imagination</li>
                            <li>Builds memory and articulation</li>
                            <li>Makes kids active</li>
                            <li>Wonderful class bonding and lots of smiles</li>
                            <li>A fun break between lessons!    </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-10">       </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <h4 class="margin-top-0"><strong>Song List - a mixture of old classics and some catchy new tunes!</strong></h4>
                        <p><i>Ants go Marching, Banana Bopalop, Buzzy Buzzy Bee, Carrot Cha Cha Cha, Caterpillar Crawl, Cowgirl Karen Kitten, Dalmatian Dots, Dig Like a Pig, Donkey Dance Party, Flap Like a Bat, Goblin Grin, Head Shoulders Knees and Toes, Hokey Cokey, I'm a Cuckoo, Old MacDonald, Ooky Kooky Spooky, She'll be Coming Round the Mountain, Skunktastic, Swanning Around and Two Can Toucan</i></p>
                        <h4 class="margin-top-0"><strong>Price</strong></h4>
                        <div class="col-md-12 padding-0">
                            <div class="col-md-10 padding-left-0">
                                Permanent class use licence for $25. Able to be installed once on a PC or Mac. No need for internet connection in classroom!
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-2">
                                <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="https://shop.skoolbo.com/ca/checkout/" class="cart">
                                    <input step="1" min="1" max="" name="quantity" value="1" title="Qty" size="4" pattern="[0-9]*" inputmode="numeric" type="hidden" class="input-text qty text">
                                    <input name="add-to-cart" value="601" type="hidden">
                                    <input name="add-to-cart-refer" value="Web" type="hidden">
                                    <input type="image" src="~/Images/brainbreaks/buyNow_btn.png" class="buyNow-btn" alt="Buy Brain Brakes now">
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <h4 class="margin-top-10"><strong>The Team Behind Skoolbo Brain Breaks</strong></h4>
                        <p>Melissa Georgiou leads a team of super-talented singers and performers from across the world. The team has more than 50 years of combined experience in teaching singing and dancing to young children. We are passionate about children being active and developing their singing and dancing skills.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-10">     </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-5"><img src="~/Images/brainbreaks/cast_fridayWorld_03.png" alt="Skoolbo Brain Brakes" class="im-responsive"></div>
