                                <h3><strong>Melissa Georgiou - Director</strong></h3>
                                <p class="text-justify">Melissa splits her time between US and Australia. She has been teaching children performing arts for more than two decades. Melissa has an extensive list of acting and directing credits, including Royal Shakespeare and Women of Manhattan.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <img src="~/Images/brainbreaks/jonathan.png" alt="Skoolbo Brain Brakes">
                            <div class="caption">
                                <h3><strong>Jonathan Geraghty - Adviser</strong></h3>
                                <p class="text-justify">Jonathan has been the Director of the Australian children’s musical group Hi-5 for the last ten years. Prior to that he directed well known tv dramas such as Home & Away and Neighbours. Jonathan believes early childhood education is a fundamental determinant of a child's future.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
