                                <h3><strong>Shane Hill - Producer</strong></h3>
                                <p class="text-justify">Shane was a teacher for eleven years prior to founding 3P Learning (Mathletics) in 2003 and then Skoolbo in 2010. Shane is deeply committed to making great learning opportunities available to all children. In 2013 Shane was awarded the global corporate social responsibility award for his impact on education.</p>
